    outlook: "The immediate outlook for Bitcoin suggests continued volatility and a critical test of key support levels. The dominant narrative of capital shifting towards AI is likely to persist in the short to medium term, potentially keeping pressure on Bitcoin and other hard assets. However, Bitcoin\'s fundamental value proposition as a decentralized digital asset and store of value remains, suggesting potential for recovery once the current market re-alignment stabilizes. The long-term trajectory will depend on sustained institutional adoption, regulatory clarity, and its ability to carve out a distinct role amidst evolving investment priorities.",
