    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual image depicting the complex and volatile intersection of AI, cryptocurrency, and traditional finance. On one side, abstract representations of AI (neural networks, glowing data streams) and crypto (blockchain links, digital coins) are merging. On the other side, traditional financial symbols (stock charts, dollar signs) are present. The merger should show both bright, innovative elements and darker, risk-laden undertones, with subtle hints of fraud or instability. Use a sophisticated, modern, digital art style with a deep color palette. Avoid clichés like robots or literal money piles. Focus on abstract concepts of data, networks, and value exchange. High resolution, dynamic composition.",
