    socialHeadlines: ["Indian markets are up! 📈 Mideast peace hopes + Jio IPO buzz. Plus, the Bank of England just dropped big news for #stablecoins. What does it mean for #India? #CryptoNews #IndianStocks", "From Sensex to Stablecoins: Tracking the latest financial shifts impacting Indian investors. BoE\'s new crypto rules could be a game-changer. #FinanceIndia #MarketUpdate", "Jio IPO excitement fuels Indian shares! But don\'t miss the Bank of England\'s critical move on stablecoins. Global finance is evolving fast. #PulseTrends #IndianEconomy", "Peace talks, IPOs, and new crypto rules! A snapshot of what\'s moving global and Indian markets today. How will #stablecoin regulation affect your digital assets? #Investment", "The world is watching: Indian markets react to global peace hopes & domestic giants. Meanwhile, the BoE is shaping the future of #crypto. Get the full scoop! #FinancialNews"],
