    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual image illustrating the convergence of traditional financial markets and the digital asset space, specifically for India. On one side, represent the Mumbai skyline with the BSE building, subtle upward trending stock charts, and a \'Jio\' logo subtly integrated. On the other side, depict abstract digital currency symbols (like stablecoin logos, but generic to avoid specific branding) with a subtle \'Bank of England\' building facade in the background, signifying regulation. Use a balanced color palette, professional and modern aesthetic, avoiding clichés. Focus on a sense of interconnectedness and future-forward finance. The central theme should be a bridge or seamless transition between the two worlds.",
