    featuredImagePrompt: "A highly detailed, professional digital illustration depicting a split scene. On one side, a stylized Bitcoin logo with an upward arrow pointing towards a \'66K\' target, set against a backdrop of a calm, optimistic financial chart. On the other side, the same Bitcoin logo with a downward arrow pointing towards a \'24K\' target, set against a backdrop of a turbulent, red-tinted stock market crash graph and a faint, stylized map of the Middle East. In a small, distinct corner of the image, integrate a subtle Dash logo overlapping a map outline of the Philippines. The overall aesthetic should be modern, clean, and convey both opportunity and risk, with a clear financial intelligence platform style. Avoid stock photo cliches.",
