      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "There is a moderate probability (55%) that bank-led tokenization initiatives will achieve some level of success, primarily in enhancing back-office efficiency and creating new regulated products, but widespread transformative impact will be slow and challenging. The probability of blockchain becoming a \'secret sauce\' for general AI applications is low (15%). The crypto market will continue its independent evolution (30%), marked by unique events and protocol developments.",
