      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "Probability-weighted, the outlook leans \'Consider\' with a significant degree of caution. There\'s a high probability (60%) of strong initial market interest due to the AI hype, but also a considerable probability (40%) of valuation adjustments post-IPO as public market scrutiny applies. The long-term success hinges on sustained innovation and effective monetization strategies amidst intense competition. Weighted towards \'Consider\' due to the undeniable growth trajectory of AI, but acknowledges substantial inherent risks.",
