      bearCase: "The \'higher-for-longer\' interest rate environment, reinforced by the bond market, will continue to increase the opportunity cost of holding non-yielding assets. Capital is likely to flow from speculative assets like Bitcoin into fixed-income instruments, leading to sustained downward pressure or range-bound price action. Any further hawkish surprises from the Fed or an economic slowdown could intensify this bearish trend.",
