    featuredImagePrompt: "A high-quality, abstract digital illustration representing the complex and diverse crypto market. On one side, subtle imagery of legal scales and handcuffs over a blockchain ledger. In the center, a stablecoin logo (like Tether\'s) transitioning or evolving. On the other side, fantastical, slightly absurd imagery of a vape device emitting digital currency symbols and AI-related patterns, all set against a backdrop of intertwining digital lines and data flows. Use a professional, tech-oriented color palette with blues, greens, and subtle golds, avoiding overt cannabis leaf imagery to maintain a financial news tone. Focus on clean lines and symbolic representation.",
