    featuredImagePrompt: "A sophisticated, high-resolution digital illustration depicting a multi-faceted financial landscape. On one side, stylized traditional bank buildings with subtle blockchain network lines connecting them, representing tokenization. In the center, a subtle, abstract representation of an AI brain with glowing neural pathways, with some blockchain elements subtly integrated but not dominating, conveying the \'skepticism\' of essential synergy. On the other side, a symbolic \'burning\' Bitcoin logo, with digital flames and a sense of value disappearing into the ether, symbolizing scarcity. The overall color palette should be professional, incorporating blues, greens, and subtle golds, with a clean, modern aesthetic. Avoid clichés like hands holding coins.",
