      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "There\'s a moderate to high probability (65%) of a slower, more institutionally-driven bull market, characterized by significant growth in tokenization and AI-blockchain convergence, but with tempered overall volatility. There\'s a moderate probability (25%) of increased regulatory pressure slowing down aspects of DeFi. A low probability (10%) exists for a return to highly speculative, rapid, and retail-led market explosions.",
