    socialHeadlines: ["Global markets are on a rollercoaster! 🎢 Fed\'s hawkish signals hit U.S. stocks while a U.S.-Iran deal sends Asian markets to record highs. #GlobalMarkets #StockMarket #Fed #IranDeal", "Big week for global stocks: S&P 500 down post-Fed, but Asia is soaring! What does the U.S.-Iran deal mean for oil & your investments? #MarketUpdate #Investing #OilPrices", "Divergence Alert! 🚨 U.S. stocks feel the Fed\'s bite, while Asian markets celebrate a new geopolitical deal. Get the full market breakdown. #FinanceNews #StockAnalysis", "Interest rates up, oil down, Asia up! The latest global market trends are a mix of caution and optimism. What\'s driving it all? #MarketTrends #FedPolicy #Geopolitics", "From Wall Street to Asia: A tale of two markets. How the Fed and a U.S.-Iran deal are shaping global stock movements. #InvestmentStrategy #GlobalEconomy"],
