      tokenUtility: "Bitcoin primarily functions as a store of value, often referred to as \'digital gold,\' due to its finite supply. It also serves as a medium of exchange, enabling global transactions, and acts as a base layer for various decentralized applications and Layer 2 solutions like the Lightning Network.",
