      keyRisks: ["Failure to achieve critical mass or widespread adoption.", "Inability to overcome internal political and competitive hurdles among consortium members.", "Rapid technological advancements in the open crypto market that outpace the bank network.", "Adverse or unclear regulatory developments.", "Significant security breaches or operational failures."],
